    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in such incredible shape, honestly looking and feeling just like it rolled right off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it tucked away and pristine, so it still has that fresh, new-car magic. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect, this is the one! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
