    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a definitive 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the S54 3.2L straight-six, showcasing peak atmospheric induction via six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering torque to the rear wheels through a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement with ARP bolts, and a complete VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from fresh bushings and a perfectly calibrated suspension geometry. Finished in Silver Grey Metallic with Nappa leather interiors showing zero bolster compression or wear, this M3 retains its factory-correct staggered Style 67 wheels. An uncompromising example for the purist seeking mechanical synchronicity and high-revving performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
